The International Settlment Association offers non proprietry Mobile phone manufacturers based upon Android OS, the ablity to licened withut fee or ongoing charges the standalone or "zero infastcuture" Coin based payment solution.
This solution is a cl;osed system, whcih prevents duplication of a digital Coin and hence all forms of double spend and the creation of any moentry value within the closed susyem.

Parties can apply to their International Settlment Association member for details and access to the required "source code" to implement a solution for deployment within their mobile phone.
